        I_AM_BUSY_WITH_PREPARATIONS_FOR_PRINCESS_CLAIDIE                        = 142,  -- I am busy with preparations for Princess Claidie's coming-of-age ceremony. You don't know what kind of vermin could be roaming the streets and looking for trouble.
        PRINCESS_CLAIDIE_S_COMING_OF_AGE_CEREMONY_IS_2                          = 143,  -- Princess Claidie's coming-of-age ceremony is about to begin at the cathedral. I must remain at my post, but why don't you attend?
        THE_KING_HAS_REQUESTED_YOUR_AUDIENCE_HE_HAS                             = 144,  -- The king has requested your audience. He has selected you from the mountain of adventurers in San d'Oria. You should feel honored!
        YOU_HAVE_MATURED_FROM_A_FLEDGLING_ADVENTURER_INTO                       = 145,  -- You have matured from a fledgling adventurer into a great asset to our kingdom. Do not let us down.
        THERE_IS_NO_NEED_FOR_MODESTY_AT_A                                       = 146,  -- There is no need for modesty at a time like this. The fate of San d'Oria is at stake!
        THE_AUTHORITIES_ARE_SAYING_THAT_A_DARK_CLOUD                            = 147,  -- The authorities are saying that a dark cloud of despair is looming over the Kingdom. They are asking for the assistance of only the best adventurers.
        I_CAN_THINK_OF_NONE_MORE_QUALIFIED_THAN                                 = 148,  -- I can think of none more qualified than you. Will you accept this mission?
        THEN_PROCEED_TO_THE_AUDIENCE_CHAMBER_IN_THE                             = 149,  -- Then proceed to the Audience Chamber in the Chateau d'Oraguille. Word has it that His Highness is not feeling that well. He may not be present for your briefing.
        SIR_LADY_THE_KINGDOM_IS_COUNTING_ON_YOU                                 = 150,  -- Sir/Lady] %! The Kingdom is counting on you. Who else, I ask you, is worthy for this task?
        AH_A_TIME_OF_GREAT_CHANGE_IS_UPON                                       = 151,  -- Ah, a time of great change is upon us. In a matter of days, the Rites of Succession will be held at the cathedral in Northern San d'Oria. It is then that the new heir to the throne will be decided.
        DUE_TO_THE_UNPREDICTABLE_CIRCUMSTANCES_THAT_TOOK_PLACE                  = 152,  -- Due to the unpredictable circumstances that took place at the princess's coming-of-age ceremony, this time, only authorized personnel will be allowed near the proceedings. However, the royal family has requested your services as a guard.
