        IT_ALL_BEGAN_WITH_A_RAINDROP_OR_SO                                      = 6874,  -- It all began with a raindrop, or so the legend says...
        MASTER_OH_MASTER_LOOK_WE_VE_SPRUNG_A                                    = 6875,  -- Master! Oh, master, look! We've sprung a leak, kupo! Just look at it drip, drip, dripping away!
        WHAT_A_TERRIBLY_TROUBLING_TURN_OF_EVENTS_KUPO                           = 6876,  -- What a terribly troubling turn of events, kupo! But have no fear! Sit tight and you'll see why I'm the most renowned handymoogle in the three nations!
        GODDESS_HAVE_MERCY_ON_MY_MOOGLE_SOUL_LOOK                               = 6877,  -- Goddess have mercy on my moogle soul. Look at this mess! Rotting roof boards! Rusted nails, kupo!
        WHY_IT_S_A_MIRACLE_THIS_TOTTERING_TUMBLE                                = 6878,  -- Why, it's a miracle this tottering, tumble-down shanty--I mean, this beautiful abode of yours--is still standing, master!
        ANYHOW_THIS_SIMPLY_WON_T_DO_KUPO_WE                                     = 6879,  -- Anyhow, this simply won't do, kupo. We must make repairs before we have water up to my little wings!
        I_FIGURE_ALL_I_LL_NEED_IS_A                                             = 6880,  -- I figure all I'll need is a good %, %, and % to have this fixed up good as new, kupo!
        COULD_I_TROUBLE_YOU_TO_TRACK_THEM_DOWN                                  = 6881,  -- Could I trouble you to track them down? While you're out, I'll patch up the other problem spots.
        AND_DO_HURRY_MASTER_LEST_YOU_RETURN_TO                                  = 6882,  -- And do hurry, Master! Lest you return to find your poor moogle friend lying prostrate in a pernicious puddle of rainwater, kupo...
        THANK_YOU_MASTER_BUT_OUR_LEAK_IS_IN                                     = 6883,  -- Thank you, Master, but our leak is in another Mog House! Bring this to me when we're back home in [San d'Oria/Bastok/Windurst], won't you, kupo?
        YOU_VE_FOUND_THEM_KUPO_I_KNEW_I                                         = 6884,  -- You've found them, kupo! I knew I could count on you. That's what I tell all my moogle buddies. Why, my master is the boldest, brightest, bestest master of them all! Now we just take these, and...
        KUPOOOOOO_THERE_YOU_HAVE_IT_BETTER_THAN_NEW                             = 6885,  -- Kupoooooo`there you have it! Better than new! Why, a bevy of wild buffalo could barge in here this second and it wouldn't budge an ilm, I say!
        WHICH_REMINDS_ME_I_WENT_AHEAD_AND_RELAYED                               = 6886,  -- Which reminds me, I went ahead and relayed the requisite reports to my manager at the MHMU.
        BUT_WOULDN_T_YOU_KNOW_IT_KUPO_IT                                        = 6887,  -- But wouldn't you know it, kupo? It seems there's been a trifling bit of trouble at one of our Rent-a-Rooms in Jeuno as well!
        YOU_KNOW_THE_ONE_RIGHT_ACROSS_FROM_DURABLE                              = 6888,  -- You know the one, right across from Durable Shields. Whatever could have gone wrong, kupo?
        WELL_THERE_S_NOTHING_TO_BE_LEARNED_LOLLYGAGGING                         = 6889,  -- Well, there's nothing to be learned lollygagging around here. Come, Master, we're off to Jeuno!
        LITTLE_DID_ANYONE_SUSPECT_THAT_THIS_WOULD_PROVE                         = 6890,  -- Little did anyone suspect that this would prove to be only the beginning of a harrowing nightmare unheard of in the annals of mooglekind...
