        IF_YOU_PROCEED_YOUR_RANK_IN_THE_GUILD                                   = 7041,  -- If you proceed, your rank in the [Carpenters'/Blacksmiths'/Goldsmiths'/Weavers'/Tanners'/Boneworkers'/Alchemists'/Culinarians'] Guild will return to that of [craftsman/artisan/adept], and your skill value will revert to the maximum for that level. This procedure cannot be undone, so please consider your decision carefully.
        RENOUNCE_YOUR_RANK_AS_A_NO_RETAIN_YES                                   = 7042,  -- Renounce your rank as a [Carpenter/Blacksmith/Goldsmith/Weaver/Tanner/Boneworker/Alchemist/Culinarian]? No, retain. Yes, renounce.
        YOU_HAVE_SUCCESSFULLY_RENOUNCED_YOUR_STATUS_AS_A                        = 7043,  -- You have successfully renounced your status as a [craftsman/artisan/adept] of the [Carpenters'/Blacksmiths'/Goldsmiths'/Weavers'/Tanners'/Boneworkers'/Alchemists'/Culinarians'] Guild.
        NOW_WHAT_BUSINESS_WOULD_AN_ADVENTURER_HAVE_IN                           = 7044,  -- Now, what business would an adventurer have in the Carpenters' Guild? This is a union for woodworkers, masons, and the like.
        THEN_I_M_GOING_TO_HAVE_TO_ASK                                           = 7045,  -- Then I'm going to have to ask you to leave. We pride ourselves in safety first here, and we don't want any visitors getting hurt, now.
        WELL_YOU_LOOK_LIKE_A_STRONG_ONE_AND                                     = 7046,  -- Well, you look like a strong one. And who knows? Maybe you'll catch on quick. Just to play it safe, we'll start you off with crystal synthesis.
        YOU_RE_PROBABLY_IN_A_HURRY_TO_GO                                        = 7047,  -- You're probably in a hurry to go off and beat some beastmen, so I'll cut the small talk. That shiny rock I just gave you--that's a crystal. I'm sure an adventurer like you has seen one before.
        EXTRACT_THE_ENERGY_OUT_OF_ONE_OF_THESE                                  = 7048,  -- Extract the energy out of one of these and you can cut, plane, join...well, let's just say, do almost anything with wood.
        I_M_NO_SCIENTIST_SO_DON_T_GO                                            = 7049,  -- I'm no scientist, so don't go asking me the details. As long as it works, we'll keep using 'em...but only on rush jobs. A good old hammer and some nails--that's where true carpentry starts.
        IF_YOU_NEED_ANY_HELP_STARTING_OUT_ASK                                   = 7050,  -- If you need any help starting out, ask the workers inside the guild. I evaluate my students on their abilities, and nothing else. You work hard, you'll move up in this trade.
        HARDNESS_ELASTICITY_WEIGHT_WOOD_HAS_TOO_MANY_MERITS                     = 7051,  -- Hardness, elasticity, weight...wood has too many merits to be able to say for certain which is best.
        WOOD_IS_THE_BODY_AND_SOUL_OF_A                                          = 7052,  -- Wood is the body and soul of a tree. Listen to what the soul has to say and let those words live on in your works. Only then will you become a true carpenter.
        FROM_THE_LOOKS_OF_YOU_IT_SEEMS_THAT                                     = 7053,  -- From the looks of you, it seems that you're ready for the next step. Make me %.
        IF_YOU_PASS_MY_TEST_I_LL_TEACH                                          = 7054,  -- If you pass my test, I'll teach you some new techniques.
        FAIRLY_NICE_WORK_I_GIVE_YOU_THE_TITLE                                   = 7055,  -- ... Fairly nice work. I give you the title of [amateur/recruit/initiate/novice/apprentice]. Work hard and never forget to be a good example to the younger students.
        I_SEE_THAT_YOUR_SKILLS_BECOME_MORE_REFINED                              = 7056,  -- ... I see that your skills become more refined with each day. I present you with the title of journeyman. You make an excellent example for the other students.
        REMARKABLE_YOUR_WORK_IS_NEARLY_FLAWLESS_STARTING_TODAY                  = 7057,  -- ... Remarkable! Your work is nearly flawless! Starting today, consider yourself an artisan. There isn't a member of this guild who doesn't know of your work.
        UNBELIEVABLE_I_VE_NEVER_SEEN_SUCH_A_SUCH                                = 7058,  -- Unbelievable. I've never seen such a...such a work of art! You are the pride of the Carpenters' Guild and worthy of the title of adept.
        IT_S_AS_IF_ALTANA_MADE_THIS_HERSELF                                     = 7059,  -- It's as if Altana made this herself. It's nothing less than a blessing from heaven. I am proud to work alongside a veteran of your caliber.
        IF_I_HAVE_TOLD_THEM_ONCE_I_HAVE                                         = 7060,  -- If I have told them once, I have told them a thousand times--if we do not start on the new weaponry, our forces will be no match for those fiendish Orcs... Oh, who might you be?
        PARDON_ME_BUT_I_HAVE_DONE_ALL_I                                         = 7061,  -- Pardon me, but I have done all I can do for you at the moment.
        HOW_PITIFUL_BEING_UNABLE_TO_AFFORD_THE_WEALTH                           = 7062,  -- How pitiful--being unable to afford the wealth of knowledge I have to offer.
        I_SHALL_HELP_YOU_HOWEVER_IF_YOU_HAPPEN                                  = 7063,  -- I shall help you. However, if you happen to falter, blame only yourself.
        FOR_AN_ADVENTURER_SUCH_AS_YOU_SHOULD_BE                                 = 7064,  -- For an adventurer such as you, % should be manageable. You will require...
        THAT_IS_ALL_I_AM_IN_THE_MIDDLE                                          = 7065,  -- That is all. I am in the middle of an extremely important project. If you have finished with your business here, I request your departure.
        SIGH_WHEN_IS_THA_GUILDMASTER_OF_OURS_GONNA                              = 7066,  -- <Sigh>... When is tha' guildmaster of ours gonna stand up tae old Ulycille?
        HEY_SOMEBODY_HAS_ALREADY_ELPED_YE                                       = 7067,  -- Hey, somebody has already 'elped ye!
        WHERE_S_THE_REST_LASS_WEEK_AH_ELPED                                     = 7068,  -- Where's the rest? Lass week, Ah 'elped this lassie for free and got quite a smack upside me head from the guildmaster. Don't want that tae be happenin' anymore now do we?
        THERE_WE_ARE_NOW_CLOSE_YER_EYES                                         = 7069,  -- There we are. Now close yer eyes...
        AN_ADVENTURER_LIKE_YE_WOULD_BE_BEST_OFF                                 = 7070,  -- An adventurer like ye would be best off wit' %. Ah make it wit these...
        IF_YE_WANT_TAE_MAKE_SOMETHIN_FANCY_ASK                                  = 7071,  -- If ye want tae make somethin' fancy, ask Ulycille. Anything else, ask me. But bide away from Ramua. She makes too mannae mistakes.
        HELLO_SORRY_BUT_I_AM_BUSY_AT_THE                                        = 7072,  -- Hello! Sorry, but I am busy at the moment! Good day!
        I_AM_SORRY_BUT_I_CANNOT_HELP_YOU                                        = 7073,  -- I am sorry, but I cannot help you at the moment!
        I_AM_SORRY_BUT_THIS_IS_NOT_ENOUGH                                       = 7074,  -- I am sorry, but this is not enough...and my services are the most inexpensive here.
        DO_NOT_WORRY_I_KNOW_WHAT_I_AM                                           = 7075,  -- Do not worry! I know what I am doing! Now please close your eyes...
