        I_HEARD_THAT_IF_YOU_TRAVEL_TO_THE                                       = 7077,  -- I heard that if you travel to the forest on a chocobo, you are likely to find good timber...but do not tell Amarefice I told you his secret.
        YOUR_SKILLS_AS_A_CARPENTER_IMPRESS_ME_AND                               = 7078,  -- Your skills as a carpenter impress me and the others of the guild. Build for me %.
        IF_YOU_ARE_ABLE_TO_COMPLETE_THIS_TASK                                   = 7079,  -- If you are able to complete this task, I will grant you the title of craftsman and you will become a true member of this guild.
