        WELL_DONE_NOW_ALL_THAT_REMAINS_IS_FOR                                   = 7834,  -- Well done, %. Now, all that remains is for you to pledge your loyalty before the royaulais. Proceed immediately to the chateau. We would not want to keep His Highness waiting.
        WELCOME_BACK_I_WAS_BEGINNING_TO_WORRRRY_THAT                            = 7835,  -- Welcome back! I was beginning to worrrry that you got lost! ...Heh heh heh! Those two buffoons were rubbed the wrong way by my letters? Hah hah! Thanks, %. You've just made my day.
        NOW_ALL_THAT_S_LEFT_IS_FOR_YOU                                          = 7836,  -- Now, all that's left is for you to talk to little Kupipi over there and have her take you to the Star Sibyl. When you'rrre done, you can tell me more about your trip.
        WELL_DONE_SOLDIER_I_CAN_TELL_BY_THE                                     = 7837,  -- Well done, soldier! I can tell by the look on your face that those two sissies in Windurst and San d'Oria weren't pleased with the letters I had you deliver. Well, that's too bad!
        IF_A_LEADER_CANNOT_STAY_CALM_IN_A                                       = 7838,  -- If a leader cannot stay calm in a tense situation, he'll pay for it with his men's lives! Don't you forget that, soldier!
        NOW_MAKE_YOUR_WAY_TO_THE_PRESIDENT_S                                    = 7839,  -- Now make your way to the President's Office! Without our leader's permission, you are nothing more than a mangy dog in a uniform! Get moving!
        I_COMMEND_YOU_YOU_HAVE_DONE_WELL_IN                                     = 7840,  -- I commend you, %. You have done well in completing the tasks I set before you. You shall make a fine soldier. Now let me present you with your %.
        THIS_LICENSE_ALLOWS_YOU_PARTICIPATION_IN_THE_TRADITIONAL                = 7841,  -- This license allows you participation in the traditional San d'Orian battle exercise known as Ballista.
        AS_THIS_SPORT_HAS_ITS_ORIGINS_IN_OUR                                    = 7842,  -- As this sport has its origins in our kingdom, anything less than victory shall not be accepted.
        AH_I_ALMOST_FORGOT_CURRENTLY_THE_REINSTATEMENT_OF                       = 7843,  -- Ah, I almost forgot. Currently, the reinstatement of Conflict is only temporary. Much has changed since it was first followed many years ago.
        BECAUSE_OF_THIS_THERE_IS_A_GREAT_CHANCE                                 = 7844,  -- Because of this, there is a great chance that many of the existing rules may be changed, and the whole system outlawed for good. If you have any opinions on the games, I suggest you are vocal with them. That is all.
        OK_YOU_RRRE_DONE_HERE_S_YOUR                                            = 7845,  -- OK! You'rrre done. Here's your %!
        WITH_THIS_LICENSE_YOU_LL_BE_ABLE_TO                                     = 7846,  -- With this license, you'll be able to parrrticipate in one of San d'Oria's old Conflict events--Ballista. I would have preferrrred something more exciting--more Mithran--but I guess this will have to do for now.
        AND_NO_MATTER_THE_GAME_THE_BEST_WILL                                    = 7847,  -- And no matter the game, the best will always win, so we have nothing to worry about! Right, %?
        OH_YEAH_I_ALMOST_FORGOT_CONFLICT_S_RRREINSTATEMENT                      = 7848,  -- Oh yeah, I almost forgot... Conflict's rrreinstatement still isn't one hundred percent official. I don't know what those politicians are worrrried about, but I guess that's why I'm not a politician.
        THEY_DID_SAY_SOMETHING_ABOUT_CHANGING_THE_RULES                         = 7849,  -- They did say something about changing the rules if the players werrre not satisfied with the current ones. So remember to speak up if you want your voice hearrrd!
        WELL_DONE_SOLDIER_I_EXPECT_THE_BEST_AND                                 = 7850,  -- Well done, soldier! I expect the best, and I give the best! Take this %!
