        WHILE_I_DON_T_THINK_IT_IS_A                                             = 7854,  -- While I don't think it is a good idea, the IRNC has decided to listen to the opinions of you adventurers in order to improve Ballista. I say, if you can't take the heat, then stay out of the kitchen! Dismissed!!!
