        A_HANDFUL_OF_NO_GOOD_NOMAD_MOOGLES_AND                                  = 7959,  -- A handful of no-good nomad moogles and Goblins were conspiring to take over the MHMU, wilfully assuming false identities in order to obtain the armor and frame us, kupo!
