        HELLO_THERE_THROUGH_MY_TEACHINGS_I_SEEK_TO                              = 11628,  -- Hello there! Through my teachings I seek to raise the awareness of San d'Oria's fine citizens.
        MY_SPECIALTY_IS_THE_ELEMENTS_AND_THEIR_CORRELATIONS                     = 11629,  -- My specialty is the elements and their correlations. Of course, those from abroad are welcome to my knowledge, too.
        VIEW_THE_CHART_OF_ELEMENTAL_CORRELATIONS_YES_NO                         = 11630,  -- View the chart of elemental correlations? Yes. No.
        AH_THAT_IS_A_SHAME_YOU_VE_BEEN                                          = 11631,  -- Ah...that is a shame. You've been taught all you need to know, have you?
        EXCELLENT_CHOICE_FRIEND_THIS_MAY_NOT_BE_THE                             = 11632,  -- Excellent choice, friend. This may not be the best place for study, but let's get started!
        EVER_HEARD_OF_THE_ELEMENTS_THE_MOST_PRIMAL                              = 11633,  -- Ever heard of the elements, the most primal forms of energy? There are eight in all.
        BEHOLD_THEY_ARE_LIKE_A_WHEEL_WITH_ARROWS                                = 11634,  -- Behold, they are like a wheel, with arrows forming a circle. This shows how the myriad elements relate to one another.
        THEY_ARE_LIKE_SIX_SERPENTS_IN_A_CIRCLE                                  = 11635,  -- They are like six serpents in a circle, each biting the tail of the one before it.
        I_WILL_EXPLAIN_SIMPLY_WATER_PUTS_OUT_FIRE                               = 11636,  -- I will explain simply. Water puts out fire, whilst the heat of fire melts ice.
        ICE_BLOCKS_WIND_WHILST_WIND_WEARS_AWAY_AT                               = 11637,  -- Ice blocks wind, whilst wind wears away at earth. Can you see it right there?
        EARTH_STEALS_ENERGY_FROM_LIGHTNING_WHILST_LIGHTNING_THROWS              = 11638,  -- Earth steals energy from lightning, whilst lightning throws its bolts into water.
        LIGHT_AND_DARKNESS_OCCUPY_THE_CENTER_THEY_ARE                           = 11639,  -- Light and darkness occupy the center. They are in mutual opposition, for one cannot be both at once.
        AH_YES_THERE_S_ONE_MORE_THING_YOU                                       = 11640,  -- Ah, yes! There's one more thing you should know: the elements are tied closely to the status of your health.
        IF_YOU_D_LIKE_TO_LEARN_MORE_I                                           = 11641,  -- If you'd like to learn more, I am willing to continue.
        ARE_YOU_READY_TO_HEAR_MORE_YES_PLEASE                                   = 11642,  -- Are you ready to hear more? Yes, please. No, that will be enough.
        VERY_GOOD_FIRE_CAUSES_DISEASE_ICE_PARALYSIS_WIND                        = 11643,  -- Very good! Fire causes disease, ice paralysis, wind silence, earth petrification, lightning stun, and water poison.
        THEN_THERE_IS_CHARM_WHICH_IS_CAUSED_BY                                  = 11644,  -- Then there is charm, which is caused by light, whilst blindness, curse, and sleep are all the domain of darkness.
        THEREFORE_ARMOR_AND_ACCESSORIES_THAT_RESIST_CERTAIN_ELEMENTS            = 11645,  -- Therefore, armor and accessories that resist certain elements also help you avoid status ailments caused by those elements.
        THAT_WILL_BE_ALL_FOR_TODAY_S_LECTURE                                    = 11646,  -- That will be all for today's lecture. Should you wish to review, just ask! I teach all who wish to learn.
        WELCOME_SAN_D_ORIA_CARPENTERS_GUILD_SHOP_AT                             = 11647,  -- Welcome! San d'Oria Carpenters' Guild shop, at your service.
        SAN_D_ORIA_BLACKSMITHS_GUILD_SHOP_AT_YOUR                               = 11648,  -- San d'Oria Blacksmiths' Guild shop, at your service!
        FINDING_YOUR_WAY_AROUND_NORTHERN_SAN_D_ORIA                             = 11649,  -- Finding your way around Northern San d'Oria? Let me show you what's where!
        VIEW_HIS_MAP_YES_NO                                                     = 11650,  -- View his map? Yes. No.
        IN_THE_CENTER_LIE_THE_PARADE_GROUNDS_AND                                = 11651,  -- In the center lie the Parade Grounds and its fountain. Round them stand Chateau d'Oraguille, the San d'Oria Cathedral, and the consulates of our allies.
        LABORMAN_S_WAY_RUNS_TO_THE_NORTHWEST_DOWN                               = 11652,  -- Laborman's Way runs to the northwest. Down there you can find great centers of industry, like the Carpenters' Guild and the Blacksmiths' Guild.
        FINE_HAVE_IT_YOUR_WAY                                                   = 11653,  -- Fine, have it your way.
        I_M_GLAD_YOU_BROUGHT_A_LETTER_OF                                        = 11654,  -- I'm glad you brought a letter of introduction, but you haven't finished your duty to Consul Melek yet. You'll need to come back once that's out of the way.
        NICE_LETTER_OF_INTRODUCTION_YOU_HAVE_THERE_BUT                          = 11655,  -- Nice letter of introduction you have there, but you've accepted a job from Consul Patt-Pott, right? Finish your work, then we'll talk! Ta-taru!
        I_LL_ADMIT_YOU_RE_ONE_OF_MY                                             = 11656,  -- I'll admit, you're one of my favorite recruits, so I've always had new missions for you. But I'm responsible for other adventurers, too!
        HENCEFORTH_I_WILL_CHECK_YOUR_RANK_POINTS_TO                             = 11657,  -- Henceforth I will check your rank points to determine whether you're ready for the next mission.
        THE_BEST_WAY_TO_EARN_RANK_POINTS_IS                                     = 11658,  -- The best way to earn rank points is to join the conquest and thereby obtain crystals.
        IF_YOU_WANT_TO_KNOW_MORE_ABOUT_THE                                      = 11659,  -- If you want to know more about the conquest, ask the lord knight at any gatehouse.
        YOU_NEED_TO_RECEIVE_ORDERS_FROM_MONARLAIS_HALVER                        = 11660,  -- You need to receive orders from Monarlais Halver in Chateau d'Oraguille for your mission to be deemed official.
        BEFORE_HEADING_OUT_FOR_GHELSBA_BE_SURE_TO                               = 11661,  -- Before heading out for Ghelsba, be sure to receive orders from Monarlais Halver in Chateau d'Oraguille. Otherwise, your service won't be deemed official.
        INTERESTED_IN_GOODS_FROM_ARAGONEU                                       = 11662,  -- Interested in goods from Aragoneu?
        WELCOME_TO_THE_PHOENIX_PERCH                                            = 11663,  -- Welcome to the Phoenix Perch!
        CARE_TO_SEE_WHAT_I_HAVE                                                 = 11664,  -- Care to see what I have?
        I_VE_GOT_A_SHIPMENT_STRAIGHT_FROM_VALDEAUNIA                            = 11665,  -- I've got a shipment straight from Valdeaunia!
        FAUREGANDI_PRODUCE_FOR_SALE                                             = 11666,  -- Fauregandi produce for sale!
        WELCOME_TO_THE_ROYAL_ARMORY                                             = 11667,  -- Welcome to the Royal Armory!
        LOOKING_FOR_A_WEAPON_WE_VE_GOT_MANY                                     = 11668,  -- Looking for a weapon? We've got many in stock!
        WELL_DONE_YOU_HAVE_OUR_GRATITUDE_WITH_THIS                              = 11669,  -- Well done, %! You have our gratitude. With this, our Kingdom of San d'Oria will surely know peace at last.
        HELLO_2                                                                 = 11670,  -- Hello!
        DO_YOU_ACCEPT_THE_MISSION_I_ACCEPT_NO                                   = 11671,  -- Do you accept the mission? I accept. No, thanks.
        THE_KINGDOM_S_INFLUENCE_IS_WANING_IN_ARAGONEU                           = 11672,  -- The Kingdom's influence is waning in Aragoneu. I cannot import goods from that region, though I long to.
        WOULD_THAT_VALDEAUNIA_CAME_AGAIN_UNDER_SAN_D                            = 11673,  -- Would that Valdeaunia came again under San d'Orian dominion, I could then import its goods!
        I_D_MAKE_A_KILLING_SELLING_FAUREGANDI_PRODUCE                           = 11674,  -- I'd make a killing selling Fauregandi produce here, but that region's not under San d'Orian control!
        ONCE_ALL_OF_LI_TELOR_IS_BACK_UNDER                                      = 11675,  -- Once all of Li'Telor is back under San d'Orian influence, I'll fill my stock with unique goods from there!
        I_D_BE_MAKING_A_FORTUNE_SELLING_GOODS                                   = 11676,  -- I'd be making a fortune selling goods from Qufim Island...if it were only under San d'Orian control!
        HAVE_A_LOOK_AT_THESE_GOODS_IMPORTED_DIRECT                              = 11677,  -- Have a look at these goods imported direct from Qufim Island!
        SAN_D_ORIAN_WOODCRAFT_IS_THE_FINEST_IN                                  = 11678,  -- San d'Orian woodcraft is the finest in the land!
        HELLO_THERE_YOU_RE_THE_ONE_WITH_THE                                     = 11679,  -- Hello there! You're the one with the introduction, eh? I'm bizzy-wizzy right now. Perhaps you'd like to talk to one of the staff?
        AH_THE_ONE_WITH_THE_INTRODUCTION_ARE_YOU                                = 11680,  -- Ah, the one with the introduction, are you? I'm quite busy, you see. Perhaps one of our staff can help you?
        GOOD_LUCK_I_WILL_BESTOW_UPON_YOU_YOUR                                   = 11735,  -- Good luck, [citizen/comrade]. I will bestow upon you your nation's Signet.
        I_CANNOT_HELP_YOU_YOU_SHOULD_GO_FIND                                    = 11736,  -- I cannot help you. You should go find a guard from your own country.
        I_CANNOT_ACCEPT_CRYSTALS_FROM_SOMEONE_WHOSE_RANK                        = 11737,  -- I cannot accept crystals from someone whose rank is still 1. I advise you to either keep them until your reach rank 2, or to use them in craftwork.
        SINCE_WE_ARE_ALLIED_WITH_SAN_D_ORIA                                     = 11738,  -- Since we are allied with San d'Oria...
        SINCE_WE_ARE_ALLIED_WITH_BASTOK                                         = 11739,  -- Since we are allied with Bastok...
        SINCE_WE_ARE_ALLIED_WITH_WINDURST                                       = 11740,  -- Since we are allied with Windurst...
        I_AM_SORRY_I_AM_TOO_BUSY_WITH                                           = 11741,  -- I am sorry. I am too busy with other matters to be speaking with you.
        AH_YOU_HAVE_BROUGHT_US_SUPPLIES_THESE_WILL                              = 11742,  -- Ah, you have brought us supplies. These will help us indeed. I thank you.
        HMM_THESE_SUPPLIES_YOU_HAVE_BROUGHT_US_ARE                              = 11743,  -- Hmm... These supplies you have brought us are too old to be of any use. We will dispose of them promptly. I do commend you for your effort. May you succeed next time.
        YOU_VE_EARNED_CONQUEST_POINTS                                           = 11744,  -- You've earned conquest points!
        YOU_VE_RECEIVED_YOUR_NATION_S_SIGNET_YOU                                = 11745,  -- You've received your nation's Signet. You are now taking part in your nation's conquest campaign!
        I_AM_A_TEMPLE_KNIGHT_I_AM_ONE                                           = 11746,  -- I am , a Temple Knight. I am one of the guards charged with overseeing San d'Oria's conquest campaign.
        I_AM_AN_IRON_MUSKETEER_I_AM_ONE                                         = 11747,  -- I am , an Iron Musketeer. I am one of the guards charged with overseeing Bastok's conquest campaign.
        I_AM_A_WAR_WARLOCK_I_AM_ONE                                             = 11748,  -- I am , a War Warlock. I am one of the guards charged with overseeing Windurst's conquest campaign.
        WHAT_IS_YOUR_BUSINESS_WOULD_YOU_CAST_SIGNET                             = 11749,  -- What is your business? Would you cast Signet on me? I want to spend my conquest points. [I want to join the Expeditionary Force./Teleport me to the E.F. area.] I want to quit the E.F./change my E.F. I want to go on a supplies quest. I have some questions... Nothing, sorry to bother you.
        WHAT_DO_YOU_WISH_TO_KNOW_ABOUT_NOTHING                                  = 11750,  -- What do you wish to know about? Nothing. Conquests. Conquest results. Donating crystals. Conquest points. The effects of controlling regions. Regions controlled by other nations. Regions under beastman control.
        ALL_THREE_NATIONS_ARE_STRIVING_DAILY_TO_PUT                             = 11751,  -- All three nations are striving daily to put more regions under their control. This is what we call conquests. You can take part in it and serve your country by defeating enemies while you have Signet cast on you.
        EACH_REGION_COMPRISES_SEVERAL_AREAS_AND_THE_NATION                      = 11752,  -- Each region comprises several areas, and the nation that rids those areas of the most monsters gains control of the region.
        NATIONS_RECEIVE_GOODS_AND_RESOURCES_FROM_REGIONS_UNDER                  = 11753,  -- Nations receive goods and resources from regions under their control.
        SO_THE_MORE_REGIONS_WE_CONTROL_THE_RICHER                               = 11754,  -- So, the more regions we control, the richer our nation becomes.
        BORDER_GUARDS_ARE_ALSO_PLACED_IN_OUTPOSTS_WITHIN                        = 11755,  -- Border guards are also placed in outposts within regions under our control. They are there to cast Signet on adventurers like yourself.
        ONCE_YOU_HAVE_YOUR_NATION_S_SIGNET_YOU                                  = 11756,  -- Once you have your nation's Signet, you will be able to acquire crystals from enemies you defeat.
        NOT_ONLY_THAT_BUT_YOU_WILL_ALSO_RECEIVE                                 = 11757,  -- Not only that, but you will also receive conquest points. You get more conquest points if you defeat enemies in regions that are not under your nation's control. These points can be used to purchase items from guards like myself.
        SO_YOU_SEE_CONQUESTS_BENEFIT_NATIONS_AND_ADVENTURERS                    = 11758,  -- So you see...conquests benefit nations and adventurers alike. We expect you to do your best to serve your country.
        YOU_CAN_SEE_THE_CURRENT_STATE_OF_CONQUESTS                              = 11759,  -- You can see the current state of conquests by selecting Region Info from the main menu. Conquest results in all regions are regularly recalculated, so you may want to check them from time to time.
        SHOPS_IN_OUR_CITY_WILL_BE_SELLING_DIFFERENT                             = 11760,  -- Shops in our city will be selling different items according to our conquest rank. The Troupe Valeriano will also visit the nation that finishes first and bring a little joy to its citizens.
        YOU_CAN_DONATE_CRYSTALS_TO_YOUR_NATION_ONCE                             = 11761,  -- You can donate crystals to your nation once you achieve rank 2. Just trade them to guards like myself, and we will ensure they are sent to the proper place.
        WE_WOULD_LIKE_YOU_TO_DONATE_CRYSTALS_TO                                 = 11762,  -- We would like you to donate crystals to your nation from now on. Just trade them to guards like myself, and we will ensure they are sent to the proper place.
        YOU_CAN_ACQUIRE_CRYSTALS_BY_DEFEATING_ENEMIES_WHILE                     = 11763,  -- You can acquire crystals by defeating enemies while you have your nation's Signet. Having Signet cast on you is also the only way of taking part in conquests.
        RANK_POINTS_WILL_BE_AWARDED_TO_YOU_FOR                                  = 11764,  -- Rank points will be awarded to you for each crystal you donate, and you may be offered new missions as your rank goes up.
        YOU_ALSO_RECEIVE_RANK_POINTS_FOR_COMPLETING_MISSIONS                    = 11765,  -- You also receive rank points for completing missions. Complete missions and take part in conquests to raise your rank and serve your country.
        YOU_ARE_AWARDED_CONQUEST_POINTS_WHEN_YOU_DEFEAT                         = 11766,  -- You are awarded conquest points when you defeat monsters while you are taking part in conquests. Select "Region Info" from the menu to check your current number of conquest points.
        YOU_CAN_PURCHASE_ITEMS_FROM_GUARDS_LIKE_MYSELF                          = 11767,  -- You can purchase items from guards like myself with your conquest points, but be warned that the number of points you spend will be subtracted from your current total.
        WHEN_CONQUEST_RESULTS_ARE_ANNOUNCED_YOU_WILL_BE                         = 11768,  -- When conquest results are announced, you will be told which country controls the region you are in at that time. Sometimes regions may become neutral, or beastmen may even gain control of regions.
        IF_WE_GAIN_CONTROL_OF_A_REGION_BORDER                                   = 11769,  -- If we gain control of a region, border guards will be placed at its outposts to help adventurers like you.
        MERCHANTS_WILL_ALSO_BE_PLACED_THERE_AND_GOODS                           = 11770,  -- Merchants will also be placed there, and goods from that region will find their way to the local shops here.
        GAINING_CONTROL_OF_REGIONS_IS_THE_BASIC_PRINCIPLE                       = 11771,  -- Gaining control of regions is the basic principle behind conquests. We need each of you to do your best, and bring our nation to the top of the ranks.
        OF_COURSE_SOMETIMES_WE_LOSE_REGIONS_TO_OTHER                            = 11772,  -- Of course, sometimes we lose regions to other nations...so we must try to take them back before the next conquest results are announced.
        AS_AN_INCENTIVE_WE_WILL_AWARD_YOU_WITH                                  = 11773,  -- As an incentive, we will award you with more conquest points for defeating monsters in those regions.
        BUT_IF_WE_ARE_ALLIED_WITH_ANOTHER_NATION                                = 11774,  -- But if we are allied with another nation, you will only be awarded the regular rate for defeating monsters in our allies' regions. On the other hand, we will award you with more points for fighting in the top-ranked nation's regions.
        OUR_PARAMOUNT_CONCERN_LIES_IN_THE_BEASTMEN_GAINING                      = 11775,  -- Our paramount concern lies in the beastmen gaining control of our regions. If too many of us are defeated in a region, the beastmen will gain control of it.
        IF_THIS_HAPPENS_NOT_ONLY_IS_IT_A                                        = 11776,  -- If this happens, not only is it a great blow to our pride, but you will be unable to acquire any crystals in that region.
        THE_BEASTMEN_ARE_A_MENACE_TO_ALL_NATIONS                                = 11777,  -- The beastmen are a menace to all nations. If they rise to power, we must all unite and drive those vile creatures from that region.
        WE_NEED_YOU_TO_BRING_SUPPLIES_TO_THE                                    = 11778,  -- We need you to bring supplies to the outpost border guards who are placed in regions under our control.
