        WHAT_THIS_IS_FOR_ME_YOU_ALWAYS_GIVE                                     = 12467,  -- What? This is for me? You always give me things. Are you sure you do not want to use it to go fishing yourself, sir/madam]?
        HEY_AILBECHE                                                            = 12468,  -- Hey, Ailbeche!
