        BUT_IF_YOU_ARE_TO_FISH_FOR_HIM                                          = 12476,  -- But if you are to fish for him yourself, you should catch him easily, as long as you've had a little practice. After all, fishing is all about patience!
        IF_YOU_DO_CATCH_THE_BIG_ONE_WATCH                                       = 12477,  -- If you do catch the big one, watch out! They say he's one feisty fish. Your skills in swordsmanship will be of greater use than those of fishing, I gather.
        I_HAVE_UNCOVERED_ALL_OF_THIS_YET_I                                      = 12478,  -- I have uncovered all of this, yet I cannot go myself. Please, sir/madam], catch him in my stead!
        THEY_SAY_THAT_YOU_CAN_CATCH_THE_BIG                                     = 12479,  -- They say that you can catch the big one in Castle Oztroja. It would be foul if someone caught him before you!
        WHAT_YOU_CAUGHT_THE_BIG_ONE_AMAZING_I                                   = 12480,  -- What? You caught the big one? Amazing! I doubt I could have done the same.
        NOW_HURRY_AND_GET_IT_CLEANED_I_HAVE                                     = 12481,  -- Now, hurry and get it cleaned! I have heard of an expert fisherman in Selbina. You should find him and ask him!
        WOW_SUCH_A_THING_WAS_INSIDE_ITS_GIZZARD                                 = 12482,  -- Wow! Such a thing was inside its gizzard? Surely I would never have caught him, for he gave even you a run for your money.
        FATHER_HOW_COULD_YOU_FORGET_THIS_SWORD                                  = 12483,  -- Father, how could you forget this sword?
        WHAT_VILBERT_IS_IN_LEAGUE_WITH_THE_ORCS                                 = 12484,  -- What? Vilbert is in league with the Orcs? Hah! What nonsense!
        I_WILL_NOT_FALL_FOR_SUCH_A_JOKE                                         = 12485,  -- I will not fall for such a joke so easily. Vilbert is taking me fishing in Jugner Forest. Be not surprised if I catch a bigger fish than the big one!
        YOU_SAW_DID_YOU_NOT_MY_FATHER_IS                                        = 12486,  -- You saw, did you not? My father is a mighty knight! I wish to become like him!
        FATHER_PROMISED_TO_TAKE_ME_FISHING_BUT_I                                = 12487,  -- Father promised to take me fishing! But I know that he is a much greater swordsman than a fisher.
