        YES_THIS_IS_INDEED_OUR_WORST_NIGHTMARE_HAS                              = 12498,  -- Yes, this is indeed %. Our worst nightmare has come true.
        THIS_IS_FOR_YOU_I_FORESEE_I_WILL                                        = 12499,  -- This is for you. I foresee I will need your help yet again...
