        WELL_THAT_S_PERFECT_I_SHALL_ORDER_YOU                                   = 12570,  -- Well, that's perfect. I shall order you to undertake this mission.
        INFILTRATE_GHELSBA_AND_DETERMINE_WHETHER_THEY_HOLD_THIS                 = 12571,  -- Infiltrate Ghelsba, and determine whether they hold this Tedimout captive. I've heard they keep prisoners in a small hut somewhere.
