        SO_TEDIMOUT_HAS_RETURNED_CONFOUND_THAT_MEDDLING_ADVENTURER              = 12577,  -- So, Tedimout has returned... Confound that meddling adventurer!
        WE_CAN_NEGOTIATE_WITH_THE_ORCS_ONCE_WE                                  = 12578,  -- We can negotiate with the Orcs once we know what they want, but I loathe the prospect of sending Temple Knights to scout.
        THAT_HOTHEADED_BROTHER_OF_YOURS_REFUSES_TO_THINK                        = 12579,  -- That hotheaded brother of yours refuses to think pragmatically. Our research through the centuries proves that the Gates of Paradise will soon open forth!
        AND_STILL_HIS_EARS_ARE_DEAF_TO_US                                       = 12580,  -- And still his ears are deaf to us! Your Highness, I fear we may fall behind the other nations.
