        I_QUESTION_WHETHER_QUEEN_LEAUTE_TRULY_PASSED_AWAY                       = 12593,  -- I question whether Queen Leaute truly passed away fifteen years past. Tell me, of what cause did she die?
        WHO_ARE_YOU_AND_WHY_DO_YOU_PRY                                          = 12594,  -- Who are you, and why do you pry with such inquiries?
        PLEASE_I_HAVE_TRAVELED_FROM_AFAR_TO_SEE                                 = 12595,  -- Please, I have traveled from afar to see Her Highness!
        YOU_VE_WHAT                                                             = 12596,  -- You've what!?
        VERY_WELL_LISTEN_CLOSELY_FIFTEEN_YEARS_AGO_QUEEN                        = 12597,  -- Very well. Listen closely. Fifteen years ago, Queen Leaute fell to a rare sickness. She left this world before we could save her.
        AH_SO_AN_ILLNESS_CLAIMED_HER_LIFE                                       = 12598,  -- Ah, so an illness claimed her life.
        WELL_IT_S_NONE_OF_YOUR_CONCERN_AT                                       = 12599,  -- Well, it's none of your concern at any rate. Even if she lived, an adventurer like you could never see her, much less the inside of Chateau d'Oraguille.
        ER                                                                      = 12600,  -- Er...
        WHAT_WAS_THE_NAME_OF_HER_ILLNESS                                        = 12601,  -- What was the name of her illness?
        WE_ARE_NOT_TOLD_SUCH_THINGS_ONLY_THE                                    = 12602,  -- We are not told such things. Only the royal family would know.
        IS_THAT_SO_WELL_I_THANK_YOU_FOR                                         = 12603,  -- Is that so? Well, I thank you for your kindness, proud knight of San d'Oria.
        HEY_WAIT                                                                = 12604,  -- Hey, wait!
        WHAT_WAS_THE_MATTER_WITH_THAT_ADVENTURER_HE                             = 12605,  -- What was the matter with that adventurer? He was awfully stubborn, wasn't he?
        HE_SEEMED_TO_KNOW_THE_LATE_QUEEN_PERSONALLY                             = 12606,  -- He seemed to know the late queen personally, but how could he not be aware of her death?
        AT_ANY_RATE_YOUR_WORK_IS_DONE_EXCELLENT                                 = 12607,  -- At any rate, your work is done. Excellent form, my friend!
        WHAT_YOU_WANT_THE_MISSION_FROM_RANK_ONE                                 = 12608,  -- What, you want the mission from rank one again?
        I_KNEW_YOU_D_RETURN_SAFELY_AND_WITH                                     = 12609,  -- I knew you'd return safely, and with the %. Mission completed!
        HAVE_YOU_EVER_SET_FOOT_INTO_KING_RANPERRE                               = 12610,  -- Have you ever set foot into King Ranperre's Tomb?
        TWO_HUNDRED_YEARS_AGO_THE_CURTAIN_FELL_ON                               = 12611,  -- Two hundred years ago, the curtain fell on the golden age of San d'Oria. Civil war erupted over the Kingdom's hegemony.
        KING_RANPERRE_WAS_THERE_TO_EXTINGUISH_THE_CONFLICT                      = 12612,  -- King Ranperre was there to extinguish the conflict. When he died he was interred in a great tomb south of East Ronfaure.
        BUT_UNKNOWN_HANDS_HAVE_DEFILED_HIS_GRAVE_OF                             = 12613,  -- But unknown hands have defiled his grave of late.
        VISITORS_REPORT_MISSING_GRAVESTONES_AND_SHADOWS_TWISTING_IN             = 12614,  -- Visitors report missing gravestones and shadows twisting in the caverns. Ravaging a royal tomb is an unforgivable crime!
        YOUR_ORDERS_ARE_TO_INVESTIGATE_THE_TOMB_AND                             = 12615,  -- Your orders are to investigate the tomb and determine if there is any truth to what they say. Do you understand?
