        PRINCE_PIEUJE_IS_IN_EARNEST_DELIBERATIONS_OVER_WHETHER                  = 12631,  -- Prince Pieuje is in earnest deliberations over whether to send Temple Knights instead. It seems his efforts are focused upon saving the children, but...
        BUT_NO_MATTER_WE_NEED_KNOWLEDGE_OF_THE                                  = 12632,  -- But no matter. We need knowledge of the enemy. You must visit the cathedral and ask what this boy looks like.
        A_BOY_TRAINING_TO_BE_A_FRIAR_WENT                                       = 12633,  -- A boy training to be a friar went near Ghelsba and did not return. His name was Tedimout.
        THE_TEMPLE_KNIGHTS_MAY_BE_MOBILIZED_SOON_YOU                            = 12634,  -- The Temple Knights may be mobilized soon. You must visit the cathedral and ask what this boy looks like.
        PRINCE_TRION_JUST_INFORMED_ME_OF_YOUR_HANDIWORK                         = 12635,  -- Prince Trion just informed me of your handiwork. You've done beautifully.
        DUE_TO_YOUR_EXEMPLARY_CONTRIBUTION_SAN_D_ORIA                           = 12636,  -- Due to your exemplary contribution, %, San d'Oria hereby recognizes you as an adventurer of rank two.
        BUT_DO_NOT_LET_IT_GO_TO_YOUR                                            = 12637,  -- But do not let it go to your head. This certificate is valid only in San d'Oria.
        WORK_HARD_AND_BETTER_THINGS_WILL_COME_MY                                = 12638,  -- Work hard and better things will come, my friend. Someday your name will be known to our allies as well.
        OH_AND_ONE_MORE_THING_THE_VICASQUE_OF                                   = 12639,  -- Oh, and one more thing. The vicasque of the cathedral said he wants to thank you on behalf of the boy.
        YOU_ACHIEVE_RANK_TWO                                                    = 12640,  -- You achieve rank two.
        AT_ANY_RATE_YOU_COMPLETED_THE_MISSION_WELL                              = 12641,  -- At any rate, you completed the mission well enough. Time for a reward!
        I_AWARD_YOU_WITH_RANK_POINTS_COMMENSURATE_WITH                          = 12642,  -- I award you with rank points commensurate with your achievement.
        PRINCE_TRION_ORDERED_SCOUTS_FROM_THE_ROYAL_KNIGHTS                      = 12643,  -- Prince Trion ordered scouts from the Royal Knights to Davoi, while Prince Pieuje ordered scouts from the Temple Knights. It's like the right hand knows not what the left is doing!
        MONARLAIS_HALVER_IS_FURIOUS_BUT_FIRST_HE_NEEDS                          = 12644,  -- Monarlais Halver is furious, but first he needs knowledge. You must find the scout from the Temple Knights, receive his scouting report, and return that report to the monarlais.
        WHAT_YOU_WERE_TOLD_TO_HAND_THE_TO                                       = 12645,  -- What? You were told to hand the % to Prince Pieuje personally?
        WELL_YOU_SHOULD_FIND_HIS_HIGHNESS_IN_THE                                = 12646,  -- Well, you should find His Highness in the cathedral.
        YOU_VE_COME_JUST_AT_THE_RIGHT_TIME                                      = 12647,  -- You've come just at the right time! Prince Trion wants a word with you. It seems he heard of you when you received your %.
        HEAD_TO_THE_CHAMBERS_OF_PRINCE_TRION_INSIDE                             = 12648,  -- Head to the chambers of Prince Trion inside Chateau d'Oraguille as soon as you're presentable!
        PRINCE_TRION_HAS_CALLED_FOR_YOU_HEAD_TO                                 = 12649,  -- Prince Trion has called for you. Head to his chamber inside Chateau d'Oraguille as soon as you're presentable!
        I_KNOW_NOT_WHAT_PRINCE_TRION_WANTED_YOU                                 = 12650,  -- I know not what Prince Trion wanted you to do, but see it through to the end! Understand?
        HELLO_THERE_NOW_S_NOT_THE_TIME_FOR                                      = 12651,  -- Hello there. Now's not the time for missions; Chateau d'Oraguille has been visited by bandits!
        YOU_MUST_MAKE_HASTE_TO_CHATEAU_D_ORAGUILLE                              = 12652,  -- You must make haste to Chateau d'Oraguille! Find Lady Curilla, general of the Temple Knights!
        BANDITS_INFILTRATING_CHATEAU_D_ORAGUILLE_IS_UNPRECEDENTED_IN            = 12653,  -- Bandits infiltrating Chateau d'Oraguille is unprecedented in history! Make haste and see Lady Curilla, general of the Temple Knights!
        OH_I_WANT_MY                                                            = 12654,  -- Oh, I want my %.
        PHSSSHOOOOOWOOOO_YOU_NEVER_SEE_GOBLINSHHH_FROM_UNDERWORLD_ME            = 12655,  -- <Phssshooooowoooo> You never see Goblinshhh from underworld? Me no bad. Me sell chipshhh. You buy. Use with shhhtone heart. You get lucky!
        I_VE_BEEN_TRYING_TO_IMPORT_GOODS_FROM                                   = 12656,  -- I've been trying to import goods from Vollbow, but it's so hard to get items from areas that aren't under San d'Orian control.
        WHAT_IS_THIS_YOU_WISH_TO_LEARN_OF                                       = 12657,  -- What is this? You wish to learn of dragons? If only Doctor Oiheaurese were...
        HERE                                                                    = 12658,  -- ...here!
        DOCTOR_THIS_ADVENTURER_IS_INQUIRING_ABOUT_DRAGONS                       = 12659,  -- Doctor, this adventurer is inquiring about dragons.
        WELL_THEN_OUR_ADVENTURER_HAS_COME_TO_THE                                = 12660,  -- Well, then our adventurer has come to the right place. First of all, young lad/lass], you must understand that where there are holy dragons, there exist dragons of evil as well.
        WHY_SIR_RAHAL_WHAT_GIVES_US_THE_HONOR                                   = 12661,  -- Why, Sir Rahal. What gives us the honor of your presence here today?
        NOTHING_URGENT_DOCTOR_I_WAS_JUST_WONDERING_IF                           = 12662,  -- Nothing urgent, Doctor. I was just wondering if anything peculiar--any suspicious characters--had been spotted in this area recently.
        NO_NOTHING_OUT_OF_THE_ORDINARY_SIR                                      = 12663,  -- No...nothing out of the ordinary, sir.
        I_SEE_I_JUST_THOUGHT_THAT_MAYBE_THE                                     = 12664,  -- I see... I just thought that...maybe the body of...his body was...no...
        CARRY_ON                                                                = 12665,  -- Carry on.
        AHEM_NOW_THAT_HE_IS_OUT_OF_THE                                          = 12666,  -- Ahem! Now that he is out of the way, where was I?
        AH_YES_AS_I_WAS_SAYING_RECENTLY_THERE                                   = 12667,  -- Ah, yes. As I was saying, recently there has been a large drop in the number of dragons born in Vana'diel.
        THAT_IS_WHERE_YOU_COME_IN_THERE_IS                                      = 12668,  -- That is where you come in. There is a rumor that a wyvern has laid an egg in the Maze of Shakhrami.
        I_WOULD_LIKE_YOU_TO_EXCAVATE_THE_EGG                                    = 12669,  -- I would like you to excavate the egg and protect it from the dragonslayers.
        TO_PREVENT_THEM_FROM_KILLING_THE_WYVERN_WHILE                           = 12670,  -- To prevent them from killing the wyvern while it is still young, we must get to the egg before they do.
        DOCTOR_OIHEAURESE_SAID_THAT_A_WYVERN_EGG_HAS                            = 12671,  -- Doctor Oiheaurese said that a wyvern egg has been laid deep in the Maze of Shakhrami. Could this be true?
        AH_IT_IS_YOU_I_AM_SORRY_TO                                              = 12672,  -- Ah, it is you. I am sorry to inform you that Doctor Oiheaurese is not available at the moment. Perhaps he has taken ill. His work keeps him up late into the evening.
        DO_YOU_HAVE_BUSINESS_WITH_THE_DOCTOR_WELL                               = 12673,  -- Do you have business with the doctor? Well, he is currently away from the cathedral.
        AND_WHO_MIGHT_YOU_BE_I_HAVE_NOT                                         = 12674,  -- And who might you be? I have not seen you around here before.
        MY_NAME_IS_YACHEMIDOT_I_AM_WHAT_YOU                                     = 12675,  -- My name is Yachemidot. I am what you would call a student of Doctor Oiheaurese.
        THAT_EGG_IS_THAT_REALLY_FROM_A_WYVERN                                   = 12676,  -- That egg? Is that really from a wyvern?
        HOW_WOULD_YOU_LIKE_TO_TRY_HATCHING_THAT                                 = 12677,  -- How would you like to try hatching that egg? The doctor has told me that it would be dangerous, but I would like to give it a try. Any true scientist would feel the same way.
        AND_I_JUST_HAPPEN_TO_KNOW_HOW_TO                                        = 12678,  -- And I just happen to know how to do it. Are you willing to help? You want to see it hatch too, don't you?
        TAKE_PART_IN_YACHEMIDOT_S_PLAN_YES_NO                                   = 12679,  -- Take part in Yachemidot's plan? Yes. No.
        WONDERFUL_TAKE_THE_EGG_AND_PLACE_IT_ON                                  = 12680,  -- Wonderful! Take the egg and place it on the far eastern tip of Drogaroga's Spine located in the Meriphataud Mountains.
        IT_S_NOT_THAT_DIFFICULT_ALL_YOU_HAVE                                    = 12681,  -- It's not that difficult! All you have to do is take the egg and place it on the far eastern tip of Drogaroga's Spine, which is located in the Meriphataud Mountains.
        IF_THAT_WYVERN_HAS_THE_HOLY_CREST_THEN                                  = 12682,  -- If that wyvern has the holy crest, then there's a possibility that a new dragoon may be born!
        I_VE_NEVER_HEARD_THE_DOCTOR_MENTION_ANY                                 = 12683,  -- I've never heard the Doctor mention any Yachemidot. And what is all this with placing the egg on the far eastern tip of Drogaroga's Spine in the Meriphataud Mountains?
        AH_YOU_HAVE_COME_THE_ROYAL_FAMILY_REQUESTS                              = 12684,  -- Ah, %. You have come. The royal family requests your assistance.
        I_CAN_ASSUME_YOU_HAVE_HEARD_OF_THE                                      = 12685,  -- I can assume you have heard of the late King Ranperre's Lightbringer. If that sword were to fall into Orcish hands, San d'Oria would have her back against the wall.
        THIS_SITUATION_MUST_BE_PREVENTED_AT_ANY_COST                            = 12686,  -- This situation must be prevented at any cost.
        WE_HAVE_TEMPLE_KNIGHTS_PARTICIPATING_IN_THE_SEARCH                      = 12687,  -- We have Temple Knights participating in the search efforts, but there is an obvious lack of manpower.
        OUR_SCHOLARS_HAVE_BEEN_COMBING_THROUGH_THE_ANCIENT                      = 12688,  -- Our scholars have been combing through the ancient San d'Orian text you retrieved, searching for any new clues.
        I_AM_CONFIDENT_THEY_WILL_FIND_SOMETHING                                 = 12689,  -- I am confident they will find something.
        IF_ONLY_THE_CATHEDRAL_S_LIBRARY_HAD_SURVIVED                            = 12690,  -- If only the cathedral's library had survived the fires of the Great War, we would not be so behind in our research on Lightbringer.
        YOUR_HOLINESS                                                           = 12691,  -- Your Holiness!
        I_APOLOGIZE_YOU_HAVE_A_VISITOR                                          = 12692,  -- I apologize. You have a visitor...
        MIND_YOU_NOT_WHAT_IS_IT_MORJEAN                                         = 12693,  -- Mind you not. What is it, Morjean?
        YES_YOUR_HOLINESS_DURING_THE_SEARCH_OF_THE                              = 12694,  -- Yes, Your Holiness. During the search of the library, we came across an ancient parchment hidden inside another book. Until now, we had passed it off as a poem written by someone long ago.
        HOWEVER_AFTER_DECIPHERING_IT_WE_REALIZED_IT_WAS                         = 12695,  -- However, after deciphering it, we realized it was a message reporting something hidden deep within the Bostaunieux Oubliette during the Great War.
        WHAT_COULD_IT_BE_THE_HOLY_SWORD_LIGHTBRINGER                            = 12696,  -- What? Could it be the holy sword, Lightbringer?
        WE_WERE_UNABLE_TO_TELL_FROM_THE_CONTENT                                 = 12697,  -- We were unable to tell from the content of the parchment, but the fact remains that this item was hidden for a reason.
        THANK_YOU_FOR_THE_UPDATE_YOU_MAY_LEAVE                                  = 12698,  -- Thank you for the update. You may leave now.
        WE_MUST_REPORT_THESE_NEW_FINDINGS_TO_THE                                = 12699,  -- We must report these new findings to the king immediately. This may shed some light on the whereabouts of Lightbringer.
        PRINCE_PIEUJE_WHAT_IF_WE_WERE_TO_SEND                                   = 12700,  -- Prince Pieuje, what if we were to send % to investigate?
        WAS_THE_FIRST_TO_FIND_THE_TRUE_RESTING                                  = 12701,  -- % was the first to find the true resting place of King Ranperre, and has the trust of King Destin. I feel a preliminary search of the area is necessary before a full-scale survey is carried out.
