        CURRENTLY_THE_CATHEDRAL_IS_CONDUCTING_PREPARATIONS_FOR_THE              = 12951,  -- Currently, the cathedral is conducting preparations for the Rites of Succession. If it were not for the outbreak at the coming-of-age ceremony, the services of the Temple Knights would not have been necessary...
