        WHAT_IS_GOING_ON_HERE_WHERE_IS_LIGHTBRINGER                             = 12987,  -- What is going on here? Where is Lightbringer!?
        WHY_THE_SWORD_WAS_UNSHEATHED_BUT_THE_GATES                              = 12988,  -- Why!? The sword was unsheathed, but the Gates of Paradise did not open!
