        TRION_GET_A_HOLD_OF_YOURSELF_RAHAL_READY                                = 13003,  -- Trion! Get a hold of yourself! Rahal! Ready the Royal Knights and track down those Orcs! Curilla! Double the patrols of the Temple Knights in the city! As for the rest of you--let us retreat to the castle so we can plan our next move. Dismissed!
