        MAY_I_ASK_YOU_ONE_QUESTION_WHY_DID                                      = 13015,  -- May I ask you one question? Why did you have my brother draw Lightbringer and open the Gates of Paradise?
        THE_GATES_OF_PARADISE_WHEN_THE_WAR_CAME                                 = 13016,  -- The Gates of Paradise... When the war came to a close and I saw with my own eyes what was left of Tavnazia, I was convinced that the only way to save the world was by finding and opening those gates.
