        WELL_THAT_WAS_INTERESTING_WHO_WOULD_HAVE_THOUGHT                        = 14593,  -- Well, that was interesting. Who would have thought that one of our festival trees would just get up and start walking around? I'm just glad that it is all over.
        HOWEVER_THERE_IS_SOMETHING_THAT_STILL_BOTHERS_ME                        = 14594,  -- However, there is something that still bothers me... It is like a dark cloud hanging over our fair city...
        I_VE_BEEN_SO_BUSY_FIGHTING_TREANTS_AND                                  = 14595,  -- I've been so busy fighting treants and spreading love to the children, that it wasn't until recently that I heard the rumors of the other smilebringers...
        I_DON_T_KNOW_WHAT_THESE_IMPOSTERS_ARE                                   = 14596,  -- I don't know what these imposters are cooking up, but if they are even thinking of laying a finger on the city's innocent children...
        I_HATE_TO_ASK_THIS_OF_A_STRANGER                                        = 14597,  -- I hate to ask this of a stranger, but you look like someone I can trust. Would you please be so kind as to search out the false smilebringer and bring him to me so we can straighten this whole mess out?
        YOU_RE_BACK_WERE_YOU_ABLE_TO_FIND                                       = 14598,  -- You're back! Were you able to find the imposter?
        YOU_LOCATED_HIM_BUT_HE_MANAGED_TO_ESCAPE                                = 14599,  -- You located him, but he managed to escape? Well, I guess that is better than nothing. Now that he knows we are on to him, perhaps he will cease to prey on the Kingdom's children.
        I_HEARD_FROM_ANOTHER_KIND_ADVENTURER_THAT_THE                           = 14600,  -- I heard from another kind adventurer that the false smilebringer was passing out strange-looking boxes to the young ones... Why, for all I know, there could be live scorpions hiding in those packages, just waiting to sting the cute little button noses of all my little friends.
        YOU_DON_T_KNOW_HOW_MUCH_YOUR_KINDNESS                                   = 14601,  -- You don't know how much your kindness means to me. You're a little old to be my friend, but I'd like you to have this as a token of my appreciation.
        WOW_THAT_WAS_PRETTY_FRIGHTENING_I_M_ALL                                 = 14602,  -- Wow! That was pretty frightening. I'm all for tree's rights and everything, but once those guys start walking around my town...
