        BUT_NEVER_FEAR_OUR_TOP_MOOGLE_RESEARCHERS_HAVE_3                        = 14628,  -- But never fear! Our top moogle researchers have created weapons that can injure these armor-thieving hooligans--the wondrous % and the marvelous %, kupo!
