        OH_AND_YOU_LL_FIND_THAT_THE_PRIZES                                      = 14636,  -- Oh, and you'll find that the prizes we have for you this time are even better than the last ones. You might even be one of the lucky adventurers who wins a spiffy, new... Ah, you'll just have to see it to believe it, kupo!
        NOW_IF_YOU_WANT_TO_CROSS_SWORDS_WITH                                    = 14637,  -- Now, if you want to cross swords with the invincible interlopers, equip % or % and talk to a nomad moogle, kupo!
