        WHAT_WHO_WAS_I_TALKING_TO_JUST_NOW                                      = 14672,  -- What? Who was I talking to just now? Oh, the other day, this really nice old man gave me my very own % so I could call him whenever I wanted. He teaches me all sorts of things, and all I have to do is call him Grandpa and do whatever he says.
