        HE_ALSO_TOLD_ME_THAT_IF_I_GIVE                                          = 14674,  -- He also told me that if I give 'em something, they'll give me % in return. I really wanted one, so I was all ready to go through that gate over there when the guard gave me a nasty loxok...
        HEY_YOU_RE_AN_ADVENTURER_RIGHT_DOESN_T                                  = 14675,  -- Hey. You're an adventurer, right? Doesn't Altana say that you guys have to help little kids or your brain will melt and bugs will eat your ears? Go out and get me %, ASAP. Don't worry, you'll get your reward!
