        DON_T_GET_THE_WRRRONG_IDEA_IT_S                                         = 17763,  -- Don't get the wrrrong idea! It's not like I enjoy the gift or anything! Just run back to % and drop dead! This conversation never happened!
        YOU_HAVE_RECEIVED                                                       = 17764,  -- You have received %!
