        HAVE_YOU_HAD_THE_OPPORTUNITY_TO_SPEAK_WITH                              = 17767,  -- Have you had the opportunity to speak with Alaune down by the Westgate in Southern San d'Oria? She is said to be a veritable treasure trove of knowledge useful to adventurers like yourself.
        YOU_THERE_YES_YOU_COME_HERE_FOR_A                                       = 17768,  -- You there! Yes, you! Come here for a moment.
