        IN_ANY_EVENT_MY_STANDING_IN_OUR_GUILD                                   = 17808,  -- In any event, my standing in our guild is safe thanks to your efforts. Please accept this % as a token of my appreciation. You have my eternal gratitude, friend carpenter!
