        IF_YOU_RE_INTERESTED_I_CAN_EXCHANGE_ALL                                 = 17834,  -- If you're interested, I can exchange all the tokens you have for a grand gift of galactic proportion, kupo! Well, perhaps that's exaggerating things a tad.
