        LEANING_IN_CLOSELY_TO_THE_DEVICE_ONE_CAN                                = 18250,  -- Leaning in closely to the device, one can make out miniscule etchings that read, Trade various crystals to this waypoint to receive kinetic units that may be used when you wish to warp to another locale.
