        SHOULDST_THY_JOURNEY_TAKE_THEE_TO_ANOTHER_NATION                        = 18267,  -- Shouldst thy journey take thee to another nation, my kindred spirits in either [Northern San d'Oria/Port Bastok/Port Windurst] or [Northern San d'Oria/Port Bastok/Port Windurst] would also suffice.
