        AS_A_MONIPULATOR_THOU_HAST_LIKELY_REDUCED_OPPONENTS                     = 18275,  -- As a monipulator, thou hast likely reduced opponents everywhere to bawling babes at the mere mention of thy name.
        SIMULTANEOUSLY_THOUGH_COMBATANTS_WHO_HATH_CUT_SWATHS_THROUGH            = 18276,  -- Simultaneously, though, combatants who hath cut swaths through adversaries while inside bestial vessels betimes yearneth for more...to bite the hand that feedeth.
        A_SAGA_SUNG_OF_THOSE_WHO_INSTILL_TERROR                                 = 18277,  -- A saga sung of those who instill terror and those who release the land from it... Bwahaha, a worthy tale of spiritual strife, forsooth.
        NOW_THAT_THE_STAGE_HATH_BEEN_SET_I                                      = 18278,  -- Now that the stage hath been set, I shall impart the extent of my gladiatorial knowledge to thee. Simply ask and thou shalt receive.
        WHAT_SHALL_YOU_ASK_ABOUT_BELLIGERENCY_RANKS_PRESTIGE                    = 18279,  -- What shall you ask about? Belligerency. Ranks. Prestige. Spoils. Domination. Nothing.
        THOSE_WHO_HAVE_THE_AMBITION_TO_SLAY_MONIPULATORS                        = 18280,  -- Those who have the ambition to slay monipulators can do battle against them by speaking with [me/my Northern San d'Orian ally] or one of my brethren in either [Port Bastok or Port Windurst/Northern San d'Oria or Port Windurst/Northern San d'Oria or Port Bastok] and receiving %.
        THIS_IS_THY_METAPHORICAL_MUSTER_AS_WELL_AS                              = 18281,  -- This % is thy metaphorical muster as well as official avowal to enter belligerency.
        WHILE_IT_DOTH_PROVIDE_MYRIAD_BOONS_TO_THEE                              = 18282,  -- While it doth provide myriad boons to thee, it preventeth not those outside thy coterie from interfering with thy duty. Such a benediction will only descend upon the yare souls who hath claimed monipulators as their prey.
        I_MUST_ALSO_CAUTION_THEE_TO_BEWARE_THAT                                 = 18283,  -- I must also caution thee to beware that, depending on thy level of expertise, it may not behoove thee to tread upon the soils of certain lands.
        LASTLY_SHOULD_THY_BLOODLUST_CEASE_OR_RESOLVE_WITHER                     = 18284,  -- Lastly, should thy bloodlust cease or resolve wither on the vine, speak to me and I shall grant thee permission to withdraw from belligerency.
        LASTLY_SHOULD_THY_BLOODLUST_CEASE_OR_RESOLVE_WITHER_2                   = 18285,  -- Lastly, should thy bloodlust cease or resolve wither on the vine, speak to one of my compatriots and they shall grant thee permission to withdraw from belligerency.
        THREE_RANKS_DOTH_SERVE_TO_CLASSIFY_THE_WORLD                            = 18286,  -- Three ranks doth serve to classify the world's monipulator executioners. There is the eponymous gladiator (Gla), champion gladiator (CG), and high champion gladiator (HCG).
        NAUGHT_ELSE_NEEDS_BE_EXPLAINED_ANENT_THIS_SIMPLE                        = 18287,  -- Naught else needs be explained anent this simple concept...save that a gladiator's rank is determined by his prestige.
        PRESTIGE_IS_THE_GLADIATOR_S_EQUIVALENT_OF_THE                           = 18288,  -- Prestige is the gladiator's equivalent of the common adventurer's fame.
        DEFEATING_BOTH_MONSTERS_AND_MONIPULATORS_INCREASETH_THY_PRESTIGE        = 18289,  -- Defeating both monsters and monipulators increaseth thy prestige, while falling victim to their claws decreaseth it.
        EACH_RANK_ALSO_HATH_A_CORRESPONDING_MAXIMUM_AMOUNT                      = 18290,  -- Each rank also hath a corresponding maximum amount of prestige, much like the infamy of monipulators.
        ASCERTAINING_THY_CURRENT_PRESTIGE_IS_MERELY_A_TRIFLE                    = 18291,  -- Ascertaining thy current prestige is merely a trifle. (Access the Profile menu under Status.)
        OF_COURSE_PRESTIGE_IS_NOT_SIMPLY_A_MEANS                                = 18292,  -- Of course, prestige is not simply a means by which to boast to thy inferiors. Thou canst cede it to me in exchange for troves of splendid rewards.
        NO_VICTORY_DOTH_TASTE_AS_SWEET_AS_ONE                                   = 18293,  -- No victory doth taste as sweet as one where the stakes are high. Flaying treacherous notorious monsters and high notorious monsters occasionally earns thee spoils of war.
        A_LITTLE_COCKATRICE_TOLD_ME_THAT_MONIPULATORS_EVEN                      = 18294,  -- A little cockatrice told me that monipulators even relinquish equipment betimes, so hold not back from slicing, stabbing, and spellcasting thy savage enemies to smithereens.
        EKE_THE_EQUIPMENT_THOU_DOST_OBTAIN_MAY_BE                               = 18295,  -- Eke, the equipment thou dost obtain may be engraved with arcane glyptics.
        EKE_THE_EQUIPMENT_THOU_DOST_OBTAIN_MAY_BE_2                             = 18296,  -- Eke, the equipment thou dost obtain may be engraved with arcane glyptics by my consorts.
        ATHWART_TERRESTRIAL_BEINGS_SUCH_AS_THEE_OUR_MEZZOTINTING                = 18297,  -- Athwart terrestrial beings such as thee, our mezzotinting process leaveth nary a scratch on extant arcane glyptics.
        IN_SOOTH_IT_WOULD_BE_PURE_IDIOCY_TO                                     = 18298,  -- In sooth, it would be pure idiocy to charge nothing for our services. However, I shan't discuss figures at this juncture.
        FORGET_NOT_THAT_WE_MUST_HAVE_IN_ORDER                                   = 18299,  -- Forget not that we must have % in order to engrave arcane glyptics, lest thou wish to incur the wrath of my people.
        THY_SOUL_PINETH_FOR_MORE_THAN_THOU_CANST                                = 18300,  -- Thy soul pineth for more than thou canst conceive. Set it free and embark upon gladiatorial exploits the likes of which Vana'diel hath never witnessed.
        AROINT_THOU_MALMSEY_NOSED_FUSTILARIAN                                   = 18301,  -- Aroint, thou malmsey-nosed fustilarian!
        WHAT_SHALL_YOU_DO_RECEIVE_RETURN_PARTICIPATE_IN                         = 18302,  -- What shall you do? Receive %. Return %. Participate in PT Content. Exchange prestige. Hear an explanation. Engage in friendly banter. Nothing.
        POSSESSING_ENABLETH_THEE_TO_ENTER_COMBAT_WITH_MONIPULATORS              = 18303,  -- Possessing % enableth thee to enter combat with monipulators. Dost thou assent?
