        THOUGH_MONIPULATORS_AND_GLADIATORS_ART_DIAMETRICALLY_OPPOSED_THOU       = 18314,  -- Though monipulators and gladiators art diametrically opposed, thou mayest shift alliance betwixt both sides of the conflict as thy humors see fit. There cannot be good without evil, and the sides shall for all eternity be in stasis.
