        GLARE_THERE_IS_NO_DENYING_YOUR_SKILL_AND                                = 18346,  -- <Glare>... There is no denying your skill and experience. I deem you worthy.
        THE_ADVERSARIES_THAT_ONCE_VEXED_YOU_AND_YOUR                            = 18347,  -- The adversaries that once vexed you and your companions are now but specks of settled dust on your trail of conquest. However, I can make them worth battling once more.
