        CHARISMA_CHR_IMPROVES_SUCH_FACULTIES_AS_THE_EFFECTIVENESS               = 18631,  -- Charisma (CHR) improves such faculties as the effectiveness of the beastmaster ability charm and the accuracy of bards' songs.
