        THE_TIME_OF_THE_HARVEST_FESTIVAL_IS_UPON                                = 18860,  -- The time of the Harvest Festival is upon us once more, and with it comes a most wondrous event: a costume contest known as the Pink Masquerade!
        SICK_OF_DONNING_THOSE_TATTERED_OLD_ROBES_AND                            = 18861,  -- Sick of donning those tattered old robes and half-rusted suits of armor? Then why not take this opportunity to dress up in something more festive--and perhaps even earn a prize for your efforts?
        AT_THE_VERY_LEAST_THE_MASQUERADE_PROMISES_TO                            = 18862,  -- At the very least, the masquerade promises to be a refreshing change from your everyday adventures. What say you?
        PARTICIPATE_IN_THE_PINK_MASQUERADE_SOUNDS_LIKE_FUN                      = 18863,  -- Participate in the Pink Masquerade? Sounds like fun! I think I'll pass.
        A_SHAME_UPON_SHAMES_TO_BE_SURE_BUT                                      = 18864,  -- A shame upon shames, to be sure. But there's still time to change your mind--the masquerade is available throughout the duration of the Harvest Festival!
        SPLENDID_LET_ME_EXPLAIN_THE_RULES_OF_OUR                                = 18865,  -- Splendid! Let me explain the rules of our little competition.
        ALL_ENTRANTS_ARE_TASKED_WITH_PUTTING_TOGETHER_THE                       = 18866,  -- All entrants are tasked with putting together the most lavish outfits they can find and strutting their stuff for the judge--namely, me. Points are awarded for the following types of equipment: main weapon, sub weapon, head, body, hands, legs, and feet.
        WE_RE_AN_EQUAL_OPPORTUNITY_CONTEST_SO_DON                               = 18867,  -- We're an equal opportunity contest, so don't think you'll be impressing anyone here with your Gjallarhorns or Idrises! Only rewards gleaned from special events are counted.
        FEEL_FREE_TO_BRANDISH_THEM_IF_YOU_WANT                                  = 18868,  -- Feel free to brandish them if you want, but don't expect me to care in the slightest.
        AS_THIS_IS_AN_EVENT_TO_CELEBRATE_THE                                    = 18869,  -- As this is an event to celebrate the Harvest Festival, entrance fees will not be charged in the form of gil, but rather sweets.
        THOSE_WHOSE_OUTFITS_RECEIVE_AT_LEAST_POINTS_WILL                        = 18870,  -- Those whose outfits receive at least # points will be awarded with a commemorative piece of attire directly from the steering committee.
        BUT_WHY_BE_CONTENT_WITH_BEING_MEDIOCRE_WHEN                             = 18871,  -- But why be content with being mediocre when you can reach for the stars? The top three contestants will have their entries displayed on these mannequins for all to see!
        THAT_S_THE_LONG_AND_SHORT_OF_IT                                         = 18872,  -- That's the long and short of it. Speak with me again if you have any further questions or would like to know what types of sweets we accept.
        UNTIL_THEN_PREPARE_YOUR_MOST_OUTLANDISH_COSTUME_AND                     = 18873,  -- Until then, prepare your most outlandish costume and come back when you're ready to be judged!
